This is a simple example/demo of creating a pyrex module for your application/
game that subclasses something from soya.

files:
  test.pyx      -      file containing all the pyrex code 
  setup.py      -      distutils script for compiling the module 
  testit.py     -      script to test our module

running:
compile the pyrex module: 
  $ python setup.py build_ext --inplace

run the test program: 
  $ python testit.py

